summary: The diff demonstrates substantial implementation of the professional space requirements. Key implementations include: ProLogin with hardcoded authentication (REQ-63), NexusOS with RADAR, WALLET, PORTFOLIO, and AGENDA tabs (REQ-64, REQ-65, REQ-66, REQ-70), Builder multi-step form (REQ-67), Subscription screen (REQ-68), AppContext updates for state management (REQ-76), App.tsx router updates (REQ-77), clickable NEXUS logo navigation (REQ-72), geolocation filter implementation (REQ-75), and BookingLocation studio validation (REQ-74). However, several requirements show incomplete or missing implementations in the visible diff.

missing_requirements.requirement: Add newly published studio from Builder to Explorer screen provider list with all configured data so it appears alongside existing hardcoded providers and is searchable/filterable
missing_requirements.reason: While the subscription screen publishes the studio, there is no evidence in Explorer.tsx that the newly published studio from AppContext is dynamically added to the providers list for display and filtering

missing_requirements.requirement: Filter blocked time slots from BookingDate component availability based on provider's agenda configuration
missing_requirements.reason: No changes to BookingDate.tsx are shown in the diff to implement the filtering of blocked time slots from the provider's agenda configuration

missing_requirements.requirement: Enhance BookingDate component to visually disable all past dates and past time slots with opacity 0.3 and cursor not-allowed
missing_requirements.reason: BookingDate.tsx is not included in the modified files list, so there is no evidence that past dates and time slots are being visually disabled
